X millennium for Dreamcast
==========================

Dreamcast port of the X millennium Sharp X1 turbo emulator.

Original X millennium site
<URL:http://www.retropc.net/yui/xmil.html>

selfbooting
-----------
how to create a selfbooting CD from plain files at
http://mc.pp.se/dc/cdr.html

put the BIOS and the font in the root of the CD.

Controls
--------
Dreamcast controller:
D-pad:		joystick movement
Analog:		mouse movement
A:		joystic button 1 ,press a key on virtual keyboard
B:		joystic button 2 ,remove the background on virtual keyboard
X:		left mouse button
Y:		right mouse button
R trigger:	bring/remove the virtual keyboard
L trigger:	
Start:		enter/exit the menu

Dreamcast keyboard:
likewise
S3: into the menu

Dreamcast mice:
likewise

